Nature of Business
Forte Oil Plc is an indigenous pertroleum marketing company with structured operations and strategic policies to continuously improve product delivery to its customers. Forte Oil is renowned for it's ability to offer it's consumers a wide range of products from the oil value chain; PMS, diesel, aviation fuel, kerosene, commercial gas and a wide range of lubricants for various automobiles and machines. A major player in the downstream sector of the Nigerian oil and gas sector, Forte Oil prides itself in delivering prompt, quality and effective services to our customers nationwide.


