AG. MD/CEO VISITS AP GHANA
African Petroleum plc - 20 Oct, 2010
Ag. MD/CEO VISITS AP GHANA Acting Managing Director/CEO, Mr. Mike Ahme recently paid a working visit to AP Ghana (APOG) to see firsthand the rapid development of our operations in the country. He was received by the General Manager, APOG, Mr. Nikita Oluade along with other key staff of the company. Mr. Ahme during his visit, met with the Chairman, APOG, General Hamidu; Director APOG, Wing Commander Owoo; CEO, Holimah Petroleum Ltd., William Tewiah and other key stakeholders in our Ghana operations. Several AP stations in the country were also inspected during his visit.
